Location information (city/state if publicly available or shared)

Usage Data

Usage data may be collected automatically by social media platforms where our content is hosted (e.g., YouTube, Facebook, Instagram). We may receive aggregated and anonymized insights from these platforms.

4. Tracking & Cookies

Cookies and tracking technologies are managed by the underlying social media platforms. Americamagujarati does not directly control these technologies.

You may manage cookie preferences through your browser or platform settings.

